text: Loreto Achaerandio (born 13 September 1991) is a Spanish rhythmic gymnast, born in Madrid. She competed at the 2012 Summer Olympics in London. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:Sportspeople from Madrid Category:Spanish rhythmic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Spain Category:Gymnasts at the 2012 Summer Olympics
